<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;1,600&family=PT+Sans+Narrow:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%include header.ejs%>
    <div class="banner"></div>
    <div class="article">
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left">
          <div class="testimonial">
            <div class="testimonial__quote">
              Arceus executed a sophisticated and complex intelligence operation that eventually led to the dismissal of the arbitration proceedings
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial__author">
              <img src="/images/forbes.png">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="type-watermark">
            <img src="/images/balance.png">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <h3 class="article__title">Litigation Support</h3>
          <p class="para-block">We at Arceus Consulting are the leading providers of litigation and conflict support services. We gather evidence and provide actionable intelligence that helps our clients in building and winning cases. We are a technology-driven enterprise powered by our vast information networks, leading digital and cyber capabilities, social engineering skills, and analytical prowess. Backed by technical expertise and extensive experience, we have successfully worked with law firms, corporates, government agencies, and HNIs by providing litigation and conflict support, hence establishing ourselves as the industry pioneer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-dual">
        <img src="../images/litigation-break-1.png">
        <img src="../images/litigation-break-3.png">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Evidence Collection and Analysis</p>
          <p class="para-block">We help our clients by strengthening their position and supporting the legal team. We gather circumstantial and fact-based evidence using state-of-the-art digital technologies such as AI, predictive and pattern analytics, Social engineering, reverse engineering , forensic technologies , and cyber techniques that enable us to identify and locate potential witnesses and unearth their motives. With our vast and modern databases, we at Arceus Consulting empower our customers and their legal teams to build an evidential foundation for their cases. Our methods for gathering evidence also include digital forensic techniques such as Lie Detection, Document Forgery checks, Audio and Video Analysis and social engineering that uncover complete intelligence from the witness/evidence.</p>
          <p class="para-title">Asset Tracing and Enforcement Support</p>
          <p class="para-block">At Arceus Consulting, we are pioneering Asset Tracing and Enforcement Support in today’s digital landscape for financial institutions, law firms, and government bodies. By leveraging cyber technologies and our digital expertise, we are pushing the boundaries of sophistication in intelligence and due diligence services.
            <ul>
              <li>Through our extensive network of global banking partners, we can identify, assess, and provide valuable intelligence on assets in any part of the world.</li>
              <li>We assist enforcement agencies in tracking cryptocurrency across the globe and finding crypto trails.</li>
              <li>We specialize in tracking and assessing the financial roots of high value investments being brought into the country from dirty sources by conducting due diligence.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
          <p class="para-title">Analysis of Interests and Conflicts</p>
          <p class="para-block">Analysing the interests and strategies of opponents, litigation partners, and involved parties is imperative to building a robust strategy in sensitive and complex situations. Arceus Consulting is a specialist in helping individuals, corporates, and organizations to identify adversaries and gather evidence of their misconduct through automated and manual interventions. We provide intelligence analysis using social engineering techniques. Using our digital expertise, we leverage social media to identify and assess vulnerabilities, evidence of misconduct, and malpractices of targets.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="image-break image-single">
        <img src="../images/litigation-break-2.png">
      </div>
      <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content section-content--left"></div>
        <div class="section-content section-content--center">
          <p class="para-title">Identifying Misconduct and Developing Leverage</p>
          <p class="para-block">At Arceus Consulting, we help our clients identify criminal actions in their counterparts’ operations, such as tax fraud, involvement with organized crime, and sanctions violations. We provide regulatory and enforcement authorities with the most advanced cyber capabilities and provide intelligence, information, and analysis in critical matters of national security. We track terror funding, bribery, funding for drug cartels by tracing money and cryptocurrency trails that are routed through digital channels on gaming portals and the dark web. Backed by our team’s fraud investigation experience, modern cyber techniques, and digital expertise, we at Arceus Consulting provide services and assist enforcement agencies in maintaining national security.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
  <%include footer.ejs%>
